{"tid":1547211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幾個抗爭貼士 麻麻睇睇","createTime":"2019-09-06T15:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T15:35:50.000Z","uid":136187,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d44b3f759a4b8e9dfd8506229e9920e843105dee","tid":1547211,"uid":136187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"分享一下幾個抗爭tips<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 交通燈</span><br />\n成日見到大家好辛苦琴高燈柱剪交通燈，咁樣好易比cctv影到，剪完政府又好易修復<br />\n不如劈開<strong>座地燈箱server</strong>，隨便係入面劈兩刀已經好甘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxdKfH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxdKfH8.jpg&h=7453e5ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 巴士cctv</span><br />\n班仆街popo經常問城巴新巴九巴拎cctv，所以唔該大家上巴士唔好鬆懈，以為安全無人影到換衫，就算係因塞路而停左係度都會影到你。<br />\n要特別講九巴，佢完全無要求popo拎搜查令就雙手送上cctv片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不知所謂<br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁多 諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e98632f6c84dfcd263b69e06cd791a56bcea09","tid":1547211,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e44f9c0870602821cb059e58d1b8ee986033ab1c","tid":1547211,"uid":136187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a98f86bec6edb30ef9d71c944a1c3171d2a70795","tid":1547211,"uid":173945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0